      <scopecontent id="aspace_3ccdc81cb8a498c2c3591daad071e078">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>The collection includes 5 newspapers dated December 8-12, 1941, with cover stories about the United States entering World War II after the Japanese attack on Pearl Harbor. Newspapers include the Los Angeles Times, New Haven Evening Register, New York Times, and San Francisco Chronicle.</p>
      </scopecontent>
